if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_sendstock')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_sendstock
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_sendstock */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_sendstock (
stockID int not null,
SKUcode nvarchar(100) null,
num int null,
boxID int null,
constraint PK_BUSI_SENDSTOCK primary key (stockID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_sendstock') and minor_id = 0)

'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_sendstock'
